=== Kuliyada Waxbarashada ===
[[Kuliyada Waxbarashada]] (Faculty of Education) ee Jaamacadda Camuud waa waaxda [[waxbarasho|waxabarashada]], tababirada macalimiinta iyo macluumaadka la xidhiidha wasaaradaha waxbarasho ee jaamacada taasi oo ku dhex taala dhismaha weyn ee jaamacadu ku leedahay koonfurta deegaanka [[Camuud]] 5 km waqooyi bari ee magaalada [[Borama]].<ref>"[[waxbarasho|waxabarashada]], tababirada macalimiinta iyo macluumaadka"</ref> 

Kuliyadani waxay ka mid tahay labada waaxood ee lagu bilaabay Jaamacada Camuud, tan kale waa [[Kuliyada Maamulka & Ganacsiga]], markii la bilaabay [[Sanad|sanadkii 1998dii]].<ref>"[[Kuliyada Maamulka & Ganacsiga]]"</ref><ref>"[[Sanad|sanadkii 1998dii]]"</ref><ref name="Kuliyada Waxbarasho ee Jaamacada">{{cite web
 |title=The Faculty Of Education Of Amoud University
 |url=http://www.amouduniversity.org/index.php/about/history-and-background}}</ref>

==== Diplomaka Labada Sano ====

[[Kuliyada Tababarka Macalimiinta]] (Teacher Training Program) waa tabobar iyo [[waxbarasho]] labo sano ah ooy Jaamacadda Camuud siiso macalimiin iyo arday laga soo xulo deegaano badan oo kala duwan oo ka mid ah [[Somaliland]] iyo [[Puntland]].
Dhinaca kale, [[sanad|sanadkii 2003da]] Jaamacada Camuud oo kaashanaysa hay'adaha EC, DANIDA, iyo CfBT ayaa waxaa la bilaabay tababar macalimiinta oo ah [[labo|labo sano]] diploma, kuwaas oo laga soo xulayo deegaanada [[Somaliland]] iyo [[Puntland]]. 
Dibloomkan labada sano ah ooy maalgeliyaan hay'adaha EC, DANIDA, iyo CfBT ayaa waxa jaamacadu ku tababartaa ardey 300 kor u dhaafaysa kuwaas oo jaamacadu dejiso aqalo ay u kireeysay isla markaana maamusho [[nolol|noloshooda]] iyo waxbarashadooda.<ref name="Diploomka 2da Sano ee Jaamacada">{{cite web
 |title=The Two Year Diploma Of Amoud University
 |url=http://www.amouduniversity.org/index.php/departments-and-units-administrations}}</ref><ref name="Kuliyada Waxbarasho ee Jaamacada">{{cite web
